missing iCloud account.

00:07:30.076 --> 00:07:31.526 A:middle
When you check the
account status,

00:07:31.726 --> 00:07:36.026 A:middle
you receive CKAccount
status no account.

00:07:36.356 --> 00:07:40.276 A:middle
