where you might encounter this
error, CKError network failure,

00:09:11.346 --> 00:09:13.336 A:middle
or if the CloudKit
servers are busy.

00:09:13.516 --> 00:09:14.936 A:middle
Or you might see
one of these errors:

00:09:14.936 --> 00:09:18.226 A:middle
