00:31:34.896 --> 00:31:39.266 A:middle
We encode our app object
to our local storage.

00:31:39.266 --> 00:31:42.156 A:middle
When working with a
corresponding CKRecords,

00:31:42.686 --> 00:31:46.766 A:middle
we want to store those
