00:33:08.126 --> 00:33:11.096 A:middle
Now, let's walk through a
scenario of what happens

00:33:11.306 --> 00:33:13.166 A:middle
when we try to modify
a party object

00:33:13.546 --> 00:33:18.256 A:middle
for which we've stored the
